---
// Roadmap component - OntoClaw teaser
---

<section class="roadmap-section py-20 border-b border-white/10">
  <div class="section-shell">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">
        Roadmap
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
        What's next?
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="border border-white/10 bg-bg-elevated rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/10 border border-accent-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5 10-5L12 2z"/>
              <path d="M12 22V12"/>
              <path d="M17 21.66V12a2 2 0 0 0-2-2V7.34l1.46-.92c.83-.83A3 3 0 0 0 3 3v4.34L17 21.66z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">OntoClaw</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-accent-cyan">The first natively ontological AI agent</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
          Neuro-symbolic architecture.
          Ontological knowledge is native — no MCP bridge needed for OntoSkills.
          The agent reasons directly on the graph.
        </p>

        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-accent-cta/10 border border-accent-cta/30 rounded-full text-sm text-accent-cta">
          Coming soon
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
